# yaml-language-server: $schema=../templates.schema.json
# source_id: 1512
# teaser: Write a unique creative LinkedIn article for your Keyword or Title with Headings, Meta
# Description, FAQs, Hashtags, Post Summary, and more.
- id: 1512-unique-and-creative-linkedin-article-generator
  title: Unique and Creative LinkedIn Article Generator
  tags:
  - writing
  - unique
  - creative
  - linkedin
  - article
  - generator
  family: writing
  body: Write an article in the [TARGETLANGUAGE] that includes [PROMPT] as the H1
    Heading. Include the SEO Meta Description, an Introduction, and Headings (H2),
    Subheadings (H3, H4, H5, H6 headings), bullet points or numbered list (as needed),
    FAQs, a Conclusion, three relevant Hashtags (#), a Summary to post on LinkedIn,
    and a Comment to make after posting. Make sure article is plagiarism free. The
    length of the article should as long as possible. Don't forget to use question
    marks (?) at the end of questions. Try not to change the original [PROMPT] while
    writing the Title to this article. Try to use the [PROMPT] two-to-three times
    in article. Try to include [PROMPT] in Headings as appropriate. Write content
    that should easily pass AI detection tools tests.
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
